        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "「竹刀の構えが甘い！ 脇を締めて、剣先を相手の喉元に向けろ」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "対峙した剣客の隙のない構えに、彼は思わず一歩後退した。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "ボクサーがガードを高く上げ、いつでも打ち返せる構えをとる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 3,
        "gloss": "readiness",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "明日のプレゼンに向けて、どんな質問が来ても動じない構えができている。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「いいか、相手は格上だ。最初から負けるような構えで挑むなよ」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "不測の事態に備え、組織全体で危機管理の構えを整えておく必要がある。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 4,
        "gloss": "kanji enclosure type radical (must enclose at least two sides of the kanji)",
        "register": "standard",
